Remarks/Remarques: Curve # 15.00 was created for 202. It is a low water refinement of Curve  #14.00 due to five open water mmnts obtained in 2021. Only measurements below 0.540 (from Curve #14.00) was used in the development of Curve #15.00. Start  date of Curve # 15.00 was after high water Apr 13 2021.

Curve # 14.00 was created for 2020 due to a low water refinement of # 13.00 below GH of 1.230m.  This curve was created to reflect a change what was indicated by an applied shift that stayed true since 2018.  So it was decided that shift no longer required as a proven curve change had occurred.
Curve # 13.00 low water refinement of # 12.00 below gh 0.592 BASED ON 2018 MEASUREMENT RESULTS ( 2 LOW MEASUREMENTS) ONLY 2018 MM'S USED BELOW GH 0.498.
Curve # 12 low water refinement of # 11 below 0.40 CMS based on 3; 2017 MM results
Curve # 11 low water refinement of # 10 below 0.560 based on 3; 2014 MM results
